Dutsen mai fitad da wuta mai launin toka a kan birnin Mexico
Ashes daga Popocatepetl volcano ya isa kudancin unguwar babban birnin Mexico.
Cibiyar rigakafin bala'i ta kasar ta shawarci 'yan Mexico a ranar Asabar da su guji volcano bayan da aka gano aiki a cikin ramin kuma an yi rikodin fitar da gas 183 da toka a cikin awanni 24.
Cibiyar ta lura da yawan tsawa da girgizar ƙasa.
Hotunan da aka yada a shafukan sada zumunta sun nuna wasu ƙananan launin toka a kan gilashin mota a unguwannin birnin Mexico kamar Xochimilco.
Masana ilimin kasa sun gano karuwar ayyukan dutsen mai fitad da wuta mai nisan mil 45 kudu maso gabashin babban birnin kasar tun lokacin da wata girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.1 ta afkawa tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumbar 2017.
Dutsen mai fitad da wuta da ake kira "Don Goyo" yana aiki tun 1994.
