Mutane 14 sun samu raunuka masu saurin gaske a zanga-zangar, a cewar manema labarai na yankin.
An ci gaba da samun tashin hankali a yankin da ke neman 'yancin kai shekara guda bayan zaben raba gardama na ranar 1 ga watan Oktoba da masu neman 'yancin kai na Catalonia suka yi, duk da cewa Madrid ta yi watsi da shi.
