Goal din Menga ya ba Livingston nasara 1-0 akan Rangers
Dolly Menga ta fara zira wa Livingston kwallo ta biyu
Matsayin Livingston ya ba Rangers mamaki yayin da Steven Gerrard ya yi nasara a karo na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin kungiyar Ibrox.
Golan Dolly Menga ya kasance mai mahimmanci ga ƙungiyar Gary Holt don hawa sama da matsayi ta hanyar sanyawa bayan Hibernian, a matsayi na biyu.
Har yanzu kungiyar Gerrard ba ta buga wasa a gida ba a gasar Premier a bana kuma a ranar Lahadi za ta fafata da Hearts, wadda ke da maki takwas a tsakaninsu.
Amma kafin haka Rangers za su karbi Rapid Vienna a gasar Europa a ranar Alhamis.
A halin yanzu, Livingston ya ci gaba da rashin nasara a cikin rukuni na shida a jere; Kocin Holt, har yanzu bai san rashin nasara ba tun lokacin da ya maye gurbin Kenny Miler a watan Mayu.
Livingston ya bar damar da za ta iya samun damar yin amfani da shi a kan baƙi masu rauni
Dole ne ƙungiyar Holt ta kasance da nisa kafin lokacin da suka zira kwallo, saboda da ikon su sun haifar da matsaloli iri-iri ga Rangers.
Scott Robinson ya yi hanyarsa amma harbinsa bai wuce bakin kofa ba; sannan, harbin Alan Lithgow ya fita waje wanda aka yi ta hanyar Craig Halkett daga bangaren gaba na kofin.
Ƙungiyar da ke gida ta yarda da barin Rangers su yi wasa a gaban su, suna sane da cewa za su iya zama haɗari ga baƙi a wasanni na tsaye.
Kuma wannan shine yadda aka samu burin da ya yanke hukunci.
Rangers sun ba da kyauta kuma Livingston ya yi aiki a cikin abin da Declan Gallagher da Robinson suka haɗa kai don su kafa Menga, wanda ya buga kwallon kuma ya zira kwallo daga tsakiyar filin.
A wannan lokacin Rangers sun mamaye mallakar amma sun fuskanci tsaro mara kyau wanda ya hana mai tsaron gida Liam Kelly aiki mai yawa.
Wannan tsari ya ci gaba a rabi na biyu, ko da yake Alfredo Morelos ya tilasta wa Kelly ya dakatar.
