Wannan magana ta zo ne bayan da wasu sassan gwamnatin Amurka suka yi sanarwa game da AI, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabara game da AI.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirinta a shekarar da ta gabata: tana son zama ta farko a cikin kirkire-kirkire a AI nan da shekarar 2030.
"Sau biyu a kasafin kudin bincike na AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, saboda sauran ƙasashe sun fi Amurka baya, kuma muna neman babban ci gaba na gaba a cikin AI", in ji Lee.
Biyu da kudade zai iya ninka yiwuwar cewa na gaba AI nasara da aka yi a Amurka, Lee ya ce a CNBC hira wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World order aka buga a wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne babban darektan Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya saka hannun jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI na kasar Sin: Face ++.
A shekarun 1980 a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya doke dan wasan American Othello tare da mafi girman maki kuma daga baya ya kasance mai zartarwa a Microsoft Research na reshen Google a China.
Lee ya amince da tsoffin gasa na fasaha na gwamnatin Amurka kamar su Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency's Robotics Challenge kuma ya tambaya yaushe ne na gaba don taimakawa gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
