An samu nasarar buga wasan neman zaben Trump a tashar YouTube ta Virginia
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin gangamin zaben shugaban kasa guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a garuruwan da ke kusa da shi kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tare da kuri'ar tabbatarwa a cikin hutu don dan takararsa ya cika gurbin Kotun Koli, Trump yana neman samun goyon baya a zaben tsakiyar zangon da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican suna fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki lokacin da aka kada kuri'a a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018 da karfe 7 na yamma ET.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a nan ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai iya magance batun shari'ar da aka yi a wannan makon ga dan takarar Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai tsauri game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i kuma ya dakatar da kuri'ar tabbatar da Majalisar Dattijai na mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su fuskanci zaben Nuwamba da sabon ƙarfin hali.
Don haka, taron gangamin da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa yana da nufin "karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da mahimmanci ga ajandarsa cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu a lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya gwammace ba a bayyana sunansa ba.
Taron na yau da dare, wanda za a yi a filin wasa na Wesbanco, zai iya tara magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya sami labaran kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, "a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu cikin wata guda, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican daga jihar West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya kasance na karshe a cikin binciken.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya goyi bayansa a cikin zaɓen", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia ga Reuters.
