Duk da haka, a ranar Alhamis Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya gaya wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa: "Dole ne a ci gaba da aiwatar da takunkumin Kwamitin Tsaro ba tare da wani banbanci ba har sai mun ga cikakkiyar, ta ƙarshe, da tabbatar da haramtacciyar makaman nukiliya".
Kwamitin Tsaro ya kara tsaurara takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun 2006 a kokarin yanke kudade ga shirin nukiliya da makamin Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma tafiyar ta ƙarshe ba ta tafi da kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa ya ci gaba, sa'o'i kadan kafin Koriya ta Arewa ta tuhume shi da yin "buƙatun da suka shafi 'yan daba".
A wani taron da suka yi da Moon a wannan watan, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe wani sansanin makamai masu linzami da kuma makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki matakan da suka dace.
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da ya nema sune tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma ci gaba da daidaita dangantaka da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna gudanar da wani darasi game da yadda za a sami isasshen hutu
A wannan shekarar, wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard yana sa dukkan dalibansa su kara bacci domin magance karuwar al'adun maza na karatun dare-dare da ake sha da maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗaliban da ke jami'a mafi girma a duniya ba su san ainihin yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre ne a asibitin Brigham da Muller, ya tsara wannan darasi, wanda ya yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko a Amurka.
Na samu wahayi zuwa ga wannan darasi bayan na yi wani jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
"A ƙarshen aji, wata yarinya ta zo ta ce, 'Me ya sa ba ku gaya mini wannan ba kafin na kammala karatu?'
Ya ce babu wanda ya taɓa gaya masa game da muhimmancin barci, abin da ya ba ni mamaki", in ji ta ga The Telegraph.
Wannan darasi, wanda aka fara a wannan shekarar, ya koya wa ɗalibai abubuwan yau da kullun game da yadda samun kyakkyawan yanayin bacci ke taimakawa aikin ilimi da wasanni da haɓaka ƙoshin lafiya.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin tabin hankali a makarantar likitancin Harvard da kuma babban darektan jami'ar kiwon lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da karatun ne bayan gano cewa daliban suna da karancin bacci a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya yana ɗauke da ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani sashe, akwai hoton ɗakin kwana inda ɗalibai ke danna kan kofunan kofi, labule, masu koyarwa da littattafai don samun bayanai game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki da kuma muhimmancin yin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya sa su kamu da ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar makarantar da gumakan da ke cikinta suna ƙarfafa masu halarta su yi tunani game da al'adarsu ta yau da kullum.
"Mun san cewa ba zai canja halin ɗalibai nan da nan ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da hakkin sanin wannan bayanin, kamar yadda muke da hakkin sanin sakamakon shan taba a kan lafiyarmu", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce, al'adar yin alfahari da yin barci duk dare har yanzu tana wanzuwa, kuma ya daɗa cewa, fasahar zamani da kuma matsin lamba ga ɗalibai da ke tattare da rashin barci, matsala ce mai girma.
Ta ce, tabbatar da cewa ɗalibai suna samun isashen barci da kuma barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama "makamin sirri" na ɗalibai don su magance damuwa da gajiya da kuma alhini, har ma su guji yin kiba, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwarsu ta shiga yanayin yunwa, kuma hakan yana sa su ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, wani ɗan shekara 19 daga California wanda ke nazarin ilmin sunadarai da ilimin kimiyyar lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara wannan darasi, bayan ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin darussansa a bara a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya sa ya soma wani darasi a dukan makarantar.
Mataki na gaba, ya ce, shi ne a nemi duk daliban da ke karatun digiri na biyu su kammala irin wannan tsarin karatun kafin su shiga makarantar da ake takara.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai suyi la'akari da zaɓin saita ƙararrawa don kwantawa da lokacin da za su farka. Har ila yau, yana da kyau su san illolin "hasken shuɗi" da allon lantarki da hasken LED ke fitarwa, wanda zai iya daidaita yanayin circadian kuma ya haifar da matsalolin barci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: kwallon Menga ta kori mutanen Gerrard
Rangers sun sha wahala wani mummunan labari lokacin da harin Dolly Menga ya kori Steven Gerrard da aka yi wa rauni a cikin 1-0 a Livingston.
Kungiyar Ibrox ta yi niyyar samun nasarar cin nasara a gida tun bayan nasarar 4-1 a watan Fabrairu a St Johnstone, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta jawo rashin nasarar Gerrard a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin, wanda ya bar ta da maki takwas daga Hearts, shugabannin Ladbrokes Premiership, gasar cin kofin Scotland.
Menga ya kai hari minti bakwai kafin hutu kuma Rangers da aka tsara tare da kadan daga cikin wahayi bai taba ba da ra'ayi cewa zai kasance daidai ba.
Yayin da Rangers suka sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa matsayi na uku kuma yana baya ne kawai a bayan Hibernian tare da burin burin.
Kuma zai iya zama mafi muni ga Rangers bayan da alkalin wasa Calum Spence ya sami magani don rauni a kansa bayan da aka ce ya jefa wani abu.
Gerrard ya yi canje-canje takwas a kan tawagar da ta doke Ayr a wasan kusa da karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred, gasar cin kofin Ingila ta Scotland.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt ya zo da wannan 11 na Livingston wanda ya ba da wata alama ga Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda ƙungiyarsa ta tsara ta shawo kan abokan hamayyarta a kowane lokaci.
Rangers na iya zama masu iko da mallakar, amma Livingston ya yi fiye da haka lokacin da suke da kwallon.
Da sun iya cin kwallo cikin mintuna biyu lokacin da gajeren bugun da Menga ya yi a farkon wasan ya tura Scott Pittman zuwa bakin kofin Allan McGregor, amma dan wasan ya bata wannan babbar dama.
Keaghan Jacobs ya buga kwallo mai karfi daga hannun kyaftin Craig Halkett, amma abokin aikinsa Alan Lithgow ya samu nasarar buga shi a raga ta biyu.
Rangers sun ci gaba da sarrafawa, amma kamar dai suna da bege fiye da imani game da wasansu a filin wasa.
Babu shakka, Alfredo Morelos ya ji cewa ya kamata su buga kwallo a minti 15 lokacin da shi da Steven Lawless suka yi karo, amma alkalin wasa, Steven Thomson, ya yi watsi da korafin ɗan Colombia.
Rangers sun buga kwallo biyu ne kawai a raga a farkon rabin, amma tsohon mai tsaron ragar Ibrox, Liam Kelly, ya yi fama da bugun kai na Lassana Coulibaly da kuma harin da Ovie Ejaria ya yi.
Duk da cewa buɗewar Livingston a minti na 34 na iya zama ya saɓa wa tsarin wasan, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan saboda aiki tuƙuru da suka yi.
Rangers sun sake kasawa a gaban Jacobs mai karfi.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya sanya kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya ci gaba da kasancewa mai sanyi don zaɓar Menga don yin wasa.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu ta hanyar maye gurbin Coulibaly da Ryan Kent, canjin da ya yi tasiri nan da nan lokacin da hagu ya ba da izinin zuwa Morelos, amma Kelly mai girma ya gudu daga layinsa don toshe shi.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da cinye baƙi ta hanyar yin irin wasan da suke so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna tattara dogon ball bayan daya.
Holt zai iya samun damar samun nasara a cikin minti na ƙarshe, amma McGregor ya tashi tsaye don ya kori Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya kai daga kusurwa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers Glenn Middleton ya nemi wani fanareti a lokacin da ya shiga cikin Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake yin watsi da shi.
Almanac: Mai kirkiro da Geiger counter
Yanzu kuma shafi na 30 ga Satumba, 1882 a cikin littafinmu na "Sunday Morning Almanac" shekaru 136 da suka gabata, kuma a yau, a wannan ranar ne aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na gaba Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta ganowa da kuma auna rediyo, wani abu da ya haifar da shi zuwa na'urar da aka sani da Geiger counter.
A matsayin ginshiƙin kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger counter ya zama babban mahimmin al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda yake a cikin fim ɗin 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda ya nuna waɗannan masana kimiyya masu ban mamaki Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan a duniya?"
Rogers: "Wannan ma'aunin Geiger ne, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano ma'adanai masu saurin rediyo kamar uranium.
Idan ka sa waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin ƙwayoyin da ke fitowa daga rediyo daga ma'adanai".
Evans: "Ka ce, lalle ne, haƙĩƙa, yana fashewa a yanzu!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kadan bayan ya cika shekara 63.
Amma abin da aka ƙirƙira da sunansa ya tsira.
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa za ta iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki yadda za a "gani" ƙwayoyin cuta
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa za ta iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki yadda za a gano ƙwayoyin cuta kuma a kashe su
Allurar rigakafi tana koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki ya gane ƙwayoyin cuta a matsayin ɓangare na magani
Wannan hanyar tana nufin cire kwayoyin jikin mutum daga jikin mutum, kuma a gyara su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Za su iya ganin furotin da ke cikin cututtuka daban-daban kuma su sake saka shi.
Wani allurar rigakafi na gwaji yana nuna kyakkyawan sakamako a cikin marasa lafiya da ciwon daji iri-iri.
Wata mata da aka yi wa allurar, wadda ta koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki yadda za ta gane ƙwayoyin cuta, ta ga ciwonta na ovarian ya ɓace cikin watanni 18.
Wannan hanyar tana ɗauke da ƙwayoyin jikin mutum da aka yi amfani da su wajen sarrafa su a cikin wani lab don su iya ganin furotin da ake kira HER2 da ke cikin cututtukan daji da yawa, kuma su ƙi waɗannan ƙwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, daga Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce, "Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa muna da allurar rigakafi mai matukar alkawura".
Farfesa Berzofsky ya ce, HER2 tana "taimaka wa ci gaban wasu cututtuka", har da na nono da na ovaries da na huhu da kuma na hanji.
Wani irin tsarin da ake amfani da shi wajen cire ƙwayoyin garkuwar jiki daga cikin marasa lafiya kuma a "koyar da su" su yi wa ƙwayoyin cutar kansa ja-gora ya yi aiki wajen magance wata irin cutar sankarar bargo.
Kanye West ya fara magana ne a cikin goyon bayan Trump ta hanyar sanya hat na MAGA (Make America Great Again) bayan fitowarsa a shirin Saturday Night Live (SNL).
Kuma sakamakon bai yi kyau ba.
A lokacin wani shiri na Saturday Night Live, an yi wa Kanye West bulala a cikin sutudiyo bayan gabatarwar da ta rikice inda ya yaba wa shugaban Amurka, Donald Trump kuma ya ce zai tsaya takara a 2020.
Bayan ta yi waƙar ta uku a daren, mai suna Ghost Town ("Ghost Town"), a cikin abin da ta sa wani hat na Make America Great Again, ta soki 'yan Democrat kuma ta sake tabbatar da goyon bayanta ga Trump.
"Sau da yawa ina magana da fararen fata kuma ina cewa, 'Ta yaya za ku so Trump idan ya kasance mai wariyar launin fata?'
Idan na damu da wariyar launin fata, da na bar Amurka da dadewa", in ji shi.
SNL ta fara shirin ne da satire wanda Matt Damon ya yi, inda tauraron Hollywood ya yi ba'a da shaidar Brett Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai game da zargin cin zarafin Christine Blasey Ford.
Ko da yake ba a watsa shi ba, Chris Rock ya wallafa hotunan West a shafukan sada zumunta.
Ba a bayyana ko Rock yana ƙoƙarin yin ba'a da West tare da wannan rubutun ba.
Bugu da ƙari, West ya yi gunaguni ga masu sauraro cewa yana da mummunan lokaci a bayan fage saboda hatinsa.
"An yi mini fyade a bayan fage.
Suka ce, 'Kada ka fita da wannan hat.'
Sun tsoratar da ni!
Sai suka ce ina tafiya ne don in yi busar", in ji Washington Examiner.
West ya ci gaba, "Kana son ganin yadda zan yi da kaina?" yana cewa zan "sa mini kwalkwali na Superman, saboda yana nufin ba za ka iya gaya mini abin da zan yi ba.
Ka yi ƙoƙari ka ƙaunaci".
Maganarsa ta haifar da rikice-rikice a cikin masu sauraro a kalla sau biyu kuma 'yan wasan kwaikwayo na SNL sun kasance masu jin kunya, ya ruwaito mujallar Variety, tare da shaidar da wani ya ba da labari: "Dukan ɗakin ya yi shiru".
An nada West a matsayin mataimakiyar Ariana Grande, wadda tsohon saurayin ta, mawaki Mac Miller, ya mutu kwanakin baya.
West ya ba da mutane da yawa mamaki tare da fassarar waƙar I Love It, wanda yake kama da kwalban ruwa na Perrier.
West ya samu goyon bayan shugaban kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta TPUSA, Candace Turner, wacce ta rubuta wannan sakon a shafin Twitter: "Ga daya daga cikin jarumawan da suka fi karfin gwiwa: Na gode da tsayawa kan Mafia"
Duk da haka, mai gabatar da shirin hira, Karen Hunter, ta rubuta a cikin tweet cewa West yana "zama wanda yake kuma wannan abin ban mamaki ne".
"Duk da haka, na zabi ba zan ba da lada ga kowa ba (ta hanyar siyan kiɗanku ko tufafinku ko tallafawa "fasaharku") wanda nake tsammanin yana karɓar da yada akidar da ke cutar da al'ummata.
Yana da free.
Kamar yadda muke yi", in ji shi.
Kafin wasan kwaikwayon, rapper ya sanar a Twitter cewa ya canza sunansa, yana cewa yanzu shi ne "wanda aka sani da Kanye West".
Ba shi ne na farko da ya canza sunansa ba; ya bi sawun Diddy, wanda aka fi sani da Puff Daddy, Puffy da P Diddy.
Mawaki Snoop Dogg ya kasance mai suna Snoop Lion kuma, ba shakka, jaridar mawaƙa ta ƙarshe, Prince, ta canza sunansa zuwa alama kuma daga bisani, mai zane wanda aka sani da Prince.
