Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, Kit Harington, ya kai hari ga mutum mai guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na HBO Game of Thrones.
Dan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya kai hari kan stereotype na jarumi mai tsattsauran ra'ayi, yana cewa irin wannan rawar a allon tana nuna cewa ya zama kamar matasa suna da wuya su girmama su.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce "wani abu ya ɓace" kuma yana mamakin yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa a cikin zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri mai wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana jin "ƙarfi" don magance matsalar.
