Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya, kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState, sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano asalin abubuwan da aka buga yana da alaƙa da sashen Waters kuma sun bayyana bayanan wani ma'aikacin Waters, Capitol Hill ya ruwaito.
"Wannan tuhuma ba ta da tushe kuma ƙarya ce", Waters ya ci gaba.
