Johnny English ya sake yin aiki, mai ba da labari game da Rowan Atkinson
Ya zama al'ada don neman ƙetare Brexit a cikin sabbin fina-finai daga mahangar Burtaniya kuma da alama wannan na iya amfani da shi ga dawowar wannan kamfani na wasan kwaikwayo da wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya dawo rayuwa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn (Johnny English Returns).
Shin za a juya satire mai ban dariya game da batun da yake a fili cewa mu wawaye ne a cikin sabuwar damar fitar da kaya ta kasar?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English's m, mai idanu masu tsalle da fuskar roba ya sake sabunta lasisinsa don lalata abubuwa a karo na biyu.
Hakika, shi ne wakilin sirri wanda, duk da cewa yana da kyawawan halayen kyawawan halaye, yana da ɗan Clouseau, da Mr. Bean da kuma irin wannan abu wanda ya ba da gudummawar kawai a kan motsi na motoci na wuta a bikin bude gasar Olympics na London 2012.
Hakanan an samo asali ne daga asalin duniya da kuma sirrin jami'in kasa da kasa wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin wasa a cikin tallan talabijin na Barclaycard da aka manta da su, wanda ya haifar da rikici a hanyarsa.
Akwai wasu lokuta masu kyau a cikin Johnny English na karshe.
Ina son lokacin da Johnny English ya kusanci wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu yana sanye da kayan adon da aka yi amfani da shi a zamanin da kuma lokacin da ƙafafun rotor suka yi ta bugun gaba a kan jirginsa.
Kyautar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na jiki ya tashi a gani, amma yana ba da ra'ayi cewa wasan kwaikwayo ba shi da ƙarfi kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman ma lokacin da irin waɗannan fina-finai "mai tsanani", kamar 007 da Mission Impossible, sun riga sun yi amfani da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin ɗaya daga cikin abubuwan da ke ciki.
Kamar dai an yi amfani da wasan kwaikwayo ga yara, maimakon manya, kuma a ganina, Johnny English ya yi ban mamaki ba tare da kwarewa ba ko kuma ya mayar da hankali ga wasan kwaikwayo na Atkinson a matsayin Bean.
Yanzu dai, hujja ce da ke ci gaba da kasancewa cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani dan leken asiri ya kutsa cikin babbar hanyar leken asiri ta yanar gizo ta Burtaniya kuma ya bayyana sunayen dukkan jami'an Burtaniya a yankin, abin takaici ga jami'in da ke aiki, wani karamin rawar da Kevin Eldon ya taka.
Wannan shine babban abin da ya faru ga firaminista mai girman kai da rikici, wanda ke fama da rikice-rikice na rashin amincewa da siyasa: Emma Thompson tana da kyau a cikin wannan halin da yake kama da Theresa May, amma ba za a iya yin yawa ba tare da rubutun.
Masu ba da shawara kan leken asirinsa sun sanar da shi cewa tun da yake duk masu leken asirin da ke aiki sun yi alkawarin, dole ne ya cire wani daga cikin 'yan sanda.
Kuma wannan ya shafi Johnny English wanda ba shi da kwarewa, wanda yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malami a wata makarantar da ba ta da kyau, amma yana koyar da darussan da ba a san shi ba game da yadda za a zama wakili a cikin gida; a cikin wannan ɓangaren akwai wasu barkwanci, lokacin da Turanci ya ba da makarantar leken asiri ga makarantar dutse.
An dawo da Turanci zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa kuma ya sadu da tsohon abokin aikinsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Bough yanzu mutum ne da ya auri kyaftin din jirgin ruwa, rawar da Vicki Pepperdine ke da sha'awar.
Don haka Batman da Robin daga cikin ɓarnatattun ayyukan Sirrin Sarautarsa sun dawo cikin aiki, suna fuskantar kyakkyawar mace mai ban mamaki Olga Kurylenko, Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, Firaministan kasar na fuskantar mummunan yanayi na samun damar shiga cikin duniyar mai fasaha mai karfin gaske wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Birtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
Turanci da Bough sun fara tafiya ta hanyar yin wauta: suna yin ado kamar masu hidima, suna ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai kyau; suna haifar da rikici wanda ya sa su shiga cikin jirgin ruwa na Volta; kuma Turanci ya haifar da cikakkiyar rashin adalci ta hanyar ƙoƙarin amfani da kwalliyar gaskiya ta kama-da-wane don sanin abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
Hakika, duk kama-karya an yi su ne a wannan sashen, amma a cikin irin wannan mummunan hali, kamar dai an samo su ne daga wani shirin talabijin na yara.
Sakamakon yana da daidaituwa.
Kuma kamar yadda ya faru da sauran fina-finan Johnny English, ba zan iya guje wa tunanin cewa masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da za ta yi daidai da baiwarta ba?
Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa tana shirin samar da tsarin da zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwanaki hudu a mako amma su biya su kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn tana duba wani tsari mai ban mamaki wanda zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwanaki hudu a mako amma a biya su biyar
A cewar 'yan siyasa, jam'iyyar ta ce tana son masu sana'a su ba ma'aikata karin ranar hutu daga aikin da suka samu daga fasahar kere kere.
Hakan zai sa ma'aikatan su samu hutu na kwana uku a mako, amma su ci gaba da samun albashi ɗaya.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayi zai "dace" da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin ta na karkatar da kasar zuwa ga masu aiki.
Majalisar Kungiyoyin Kwadago ta goyi bayan sauye-sauye na kwana hudu a mako a matsayin wani mataki don ma'aikata suyi amfani da tattalin arzikin da ke canzawa.
Wani babban majiyar jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa: "Ana sa ran za a sanar da sake duba manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
"Ba zai faru ba dare ba rana, amma aikin kwana hudu a mako shine burin da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar don daidaita tattalin arziki ga ma'aikata, da kuma tsarin masana'antu na jam'iyyar".
Jam'iyyar Labour ba za ta kasance farkon wanda ya goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba, kamar yadda Jam'iyyar Green ta yi alkawarin yin aiki na kwana hudu a lokacin yakin neman zaben shekara ta 2017.
Duk da haka, a halin yanzu Labour ba ta goyi bayan burin gaba ɗaya ba.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Ba a cikin manufofin jam'iyyar ba kuma ba a la'akari da shi ba".
Shugaban majalisar ministocin waje, John McDonnell, ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar Labour na makon da ya gabata don karfafa ra'ayinsa na juyin juya halin gurguzu a tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya ce ya kuduri aniyar dawo da ikon "shugabanni marasa suna" da "masu tsinkaye" a kamfanonin da ke ba da sabis na jama'a.
Shirye-shiryen da shugabar gwamnatin ta yi a cikin inuwa sun kuma nuna cewa masu hannun jarin kamfanonin ruwa na yanzu ba za su iya dawo da duk hannun jarin su ba, saboda gwamnatin ma'aikata na iya yin "rage" saboda rashin daidaito.
Ya kuma tabbatar da tsare-tsaren sanya ma'aikata a kan kwamitocin kamfanoni da kuma samar da asusun mallakar mallaka don ba da kashi 10 cikin dari na hannun jari na kamfanoni masu zaman kansu ga ma'aikata, wanda ke tattara rabon shekara-shekara har zuwa £ 500.
Lindsey Graham da John Kennedy sun gaya wa "60 Minutes" idan binciken FBI game da Kavanaugh zai iya canza ra'ayinsu
Binciken FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Alkali Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta akalla mako guda kafin a yanke shawarar zabensa a kotun kolin kasar, kuma hakan ya kawo tambaya kan ko binciken da sashen ya yi zai iya shafar 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A ranar Lahadi, a wata hira da aka watsa, 'yan jaridar "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley ya tambayi Sanata John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham na Republican idan FBI za ta iya fitar da wani abu da zai sa su canza ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya nuna cewa ya fi abokinsa na South Carolina.
"Ina nufin, ba shakka", Kennedy ya ce.
"Na ce zan je wurin shari'ar. Na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan da aka gabatar da tuhuma kuma na tambaye shi ko ya aikata hakan.
Ya kasance mai ƙarfi, mai ƙuduri, mai ƙarfi".
Duk da haka, Graham ta kuri'un da alama cewa shi ne m.
"Ra'ayina game da Brett Kavanaugh ya tabbata kuma zan yi zargin fashewa", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba; amma na san wannan: Brett ya musanta shi gaba ɗaya", in ji Graham game da Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma mutanen da ka ambata ba su iya tabbatar da hakan ba.
Hakan ya faru shekaru 36 da suka wuce.
Ba na ganin wani sabon abu".
Mene ne bikin Global Citizen Festival kuma me ya yi don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke da ban mamaki mai ban mamaki na taurari da ke aiki da kuma irin wannan manufa mai ban mamaki, don kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen Festival zai ga dubban mutane suna zuwa babban filin shakatawa na Central Park, ba kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, har ma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawar da talauci kafin 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya mai goyon bayan kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Domin samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan kuɗin VIP), masu sauraro suna buƙatar kammala wasu ayyuka ko "ayyuka", kamar yin aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga jagoran duniya, yin kira na waya ko wata hanya mai mahimmanci don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar Global Citizen ta kasance bayan shekara 12 da cimma burinta?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane da kide kide da wake-wake hanya ce ta gaske ta lallashe mutane su nemi a dauki mataki ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "clictivism", mutane suna tunanin cewa suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda kai ta yanar gizo ko aika tweet?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ya ce ya sami sama da "rabo" miliyan 19 daga mabiyansa, yana turawa zuwa wasu manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce waɗannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen ƙarfafa shugabannin duniya don sanar da alkawura da manufofi kwatankwacin sama da dala biliyan 37 da aka saita don tasiri rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 kafin 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta ambaci alkawura 390 da kuma sanarwar da aka samu daga ayyukanta, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka biya ko aka tara.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka bayar sun shafi kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta masu saka jari da masu zartarwa daga Burtaniya da suka yi alkawarin "taimaka wa yara su bunkasa zuwa cikakkiyar damar su", tare da alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don taimakawa wajen kawo karshen karancin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan karbar tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizen.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, hukumomin kasa da masu goyon bayan Global Citizen kamar ku, za mu iya juya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki zuwa tarihin tarihin", in ji jakadan The Power of Nutrition Tracey Ullman, a lokacin wani wasan kwaikwayo a watan Afrilu 2018 a London.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an dauki matakai sama da 5000 don inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga uwaye da yara a Burtaniya, gwamnati ta sanar da kudade ga aikin The Power of Nutrition wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 tare da ayyukan abinci mai gina jiki.
A cikin amsar daya daga cikin tambayoyin da aka fi yi a shafin yanar gizon, "Me ya sa kake tsammanin za mu iya kawo ƙarshen talauci?"
Global Citizen ya amsa: "Zai zama hanya mai tsawo da wahala kuma a wasu lokatai za mu faɗi kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar yadda ya faru da manyan ƙungiyoyin adawa da wariyar launin fata da na 'yancin ɗan adam da suka gabace mu, za mu yi nasara, domin tare, mun fi ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B da Janelle Monáe wasu daga cikin masu zane-zane ne da za su yi wasa a bikin na wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su gabatar.
Amurka na iya amfani da sojan ruwanta don aiwatar da "kulle" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha, in ji sakataren harkokin cikin gida na Amurka
"Idan ya zama dole", Washington na iya amfani da ruwa don hana makamashin Rasha isa kasuwannin ciki har da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ya ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi iƙirarin cewa shigar da Rasha cikin Siriya, musamman ma inda take aiki a kan umarnin gwamnati ta halal, wata hujja ce ta bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina tsammanin dalilin da yasa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shine suna son yin ciniki da makamashi kamar yadda suka yi a Gabashin Turai", in ji shi.
Bugu da ƙari, a cewar jami'in, suna da hanyoyi da kuma hanyoyin da za su magance shi.
"Amurka tana da ikon, tare da sojan ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa suna budewa kuma, idan ya cancanta, toshe su don tabbatar da cewa makamashi ba ya zuwa kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi magana da mahalarta taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta wacce ke kiran kanta "muryar mai amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta dabarun Washington na magance Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa, a aikace, iri daya ne.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki a Iran da Rasha ya fi dacewa da amfani da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yayin da yake magana game da Rasha yana cewa "yana da dabara daya" tare da tattalin arzikin da ke dogara da hydrocarbons.
An yi wannan jawabin ne yayin da gwamnatin Trump ke kan aikin bunkasa fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, domin maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ita ce mafi arha ga masu amfani da ita a Turai.
