Moscow ta ci gaba da jaddada cewa bututun mai na Nord Stream 2 na dala biliyan 11, wanda aka kafa don ninka ƙarfin bututun mai na yanzu zuwa mita biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa tsananin adawar Washington da aikin yana da dalilai na tattalin arziki ne kawai kuma misali ne na gasa mara kyau.
"Ina tsammanin mun yarda cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama kayan aiki don yin amfani da shi ba kuma masu amfani su sami damar zaɓar masu samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha, Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawar da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka, Rick Perry, wanda ya faru a watan Satumba a Moscow.
Matsayin Amurka ya sami amsa daga Jamus, wanda ya sake tabbatar da alƙawarinsa ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antar Jamus, Tarayyar Masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI), ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta janye daga manufofin makamashi na EU da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
