Elizabeth Warren za ta yi la'akari sosai da neman takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
A ranar Asabar, Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce za ta yi la'akari sosai da neman takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
A yayin taron jama'a a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa zai yi la'akari da takararsa.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatin da ta lalace kuma hakan ya hada da mace a kan mulki", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi nazari sosai kan takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi magana game da Shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin taron jama'a, yana cewa yana "kai wannan ƙasa cikin hanyar da ba daidai ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ta fito fili ta soki Trump da kuma dan takarar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
A ranar Juma'a, Warren ya yi sharhi a cikin tweet cewa "ba shakka ana buƙatar binciken FBI kafin jefa kuri'a".
Duk da haka, wani binciken da aka buga a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu jefa kuri'a na Warren ba su yi imani da cewa zai yi takara a shekarar 2020 ba.
Kashi hamsin cikin dari na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce Sanata ba za ta yi takara ba, a cewar binciken Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk da kuma Boston Globe.
Kashi talatin da biyu cikin dari sun goyi bayan wannan takarar.
Binciken ya nuna goyon baya ga takarar tsohon gwamna, Deval Patrick, tare da kashi 38 cikin dari na goyon baya ga yiwuwar takarar da kashi 48 cikin dari na adawa.
Sauran manyan sunayen 'yan Democrat dangane da yiwuwar takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa, Joe Biden, da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a hukumance kafin watan Janairu, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta ambaci matsalar damuwa ta bayan-tashin hankali (PTSD) na Track Palin a taron Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki bayan da ya shiga aikin soja a watan Satumba
A ranar Litinin da yamma, an kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da aikata wani mummunan aiki a cikin gida.
"Abin da ɗana yake fuskanta, abin da yake fuskanta a yanzu, na ga yadda ya shafi sauran iyalai da ke fama da cutar PTSD da kuma wasu raunukan da sojojinmu ke dawowa da su", in ji ta a wani taron Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta ce an hana shi shiga kurkuku kuma ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojoji "suna dawowa daban, sun taurare, suna tambayar kansu ko akwai girmamawa ga abin da 'yan uwansu' yan bindiga da 'yan saman jannati, da sauran membobin rundunar suka ba ƙasar".
An kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin mace a gida, wanda ya sabawa rahoton cin zarafin mata da kuma mallakar makami a lokacin da yake bugu, a cewar Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun ofishin 'yan sanda na Wasilla.
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun kalubalanci sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan shigar da kara game da sabuwar manufar Amurka da ke hana masu fama da tashin hankali daga gidaje ko kungiyoyin masu aikata laifi mafaka.
A ranar Juma'a, wakilan jihohi 18 da gundumar sun gabatar da rahoto mai kyau ga kotun Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka wanda ke kalubalantar manufofin, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai gabatar da kara a shari'ar Sessions da Grace v. da Kungiyar 'Yancin Bil'adama ta Amurka ta gabatar a watan Agusta ba game da manufar tarayya.
Ta ce ma'auratan ta "da 'ya'yanta' yan kungiyar masu aikata laifuka" sun ci zarafinta, amma jami'an Amurka sun yi watsi da bukatar da ta yi na neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An kama ta a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, waɗanda ke samar da manyan adadin masu neman mafaka zuwa Amurka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fuskantar matsalolin da ke tattare da ƙungiyoyin masu laifi da kuma tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta soke hukuncin da Hukumar Kula da Shige da Fice ta yanke a shekarar 2014 wanda ya baiwa 'yan gudun hijirar da ba su da takardun da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida damar neman mafaka.
Babban lauyan gundumar Columbia Karl Racine ya fada a wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na duniya".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a yanke hukunci kan duk wani bukatar neman mafaka bisa ga ainihin gaskiyar da yanayin da ake nema, kuma wannan haramcin ya saba wa wannan ka'idar", in ji rahoton da kotun ta bayar.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ci gaba da jayayya a cikin rahoton cewa manufar hana baƙi shiga ta cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna bayanin cewa suna iya zama 'yan kasuwa kuma suna "samar da ma'aikata".
A watan Yuni, Babban Lauyan Amurka Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan shige da fice da kada su ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke tserewa daga cin zarafin gida da kuma tashin hankali na ƙungiyoyin masu aikata laifi.
"Suna da damar samun mafaka ga wadanda suka bar kasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoron su saboda launin fata, addini, kasa ko kasancewarsu ga wata kungiya ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a sanarwar da ya yi a ranar 11 ga watan Yuni.
Ba a taɓa nufin mafaka ta magance dukan matsalolin da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana ba.
An yi ta kokarin ceto mutane a Palu yayin da adadin wadanda suka mutu ya ninka a kokarin neman wadanda suka tsira
Amma, ga waɗanda suka tsira, yanayin ya ci gaba da taɓarɓarewa.
"Halin da ake ciki yana da matukar damuwa", in ji mahaifiyar Risa Kusuma, mai shekara 35, tana ta'azantar da jaririnta mai zazzabi a cibiyar kwashe mutane a garin Palu.
"Kowace minti an samu motar asibiti da ke dauke da gawawwaki.
Kuma ruwan sha yana da wuya".
An ga mazauna sun koma gidajen da aka lalata, suna tattara kayansu da suka ambaliya, suna kokarin ceto duk abin da suka samu.
Daruruwan mutane sun ji rauni kuma asibitoci, waɗanda girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta lalata, sun cika.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka ji rauni, ciki har da Dwi Haris, wanda ya karye baya da kafada, suna kwance a waje da Asibitin Sojojin Palu, inda ake kula da marasa lafiya a waje saboda ci gaba da mummunar ambaliyar.
Hawaye suka cika idanunsa sa'ad da yake bayyana yadda ya ji cewa girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta girgiza ɗakin otal ɗin da yake zaune a ciki da matarsa da 'yarsa.
"Ba mu da lokacin da za mu cece mu.
"Na ji kamar bangon ya murkushe ni", in ji Haris ga Associated Press, ya kara da cewa danginsa suna bikin aure a garin.
"Na ji matata ta yi kuka don taimako, sannan kuma babu abin da ya faru.
Ban san abin da ya faru da ita ko 'yata ba.
Ina fatan suna cikin koshin lafiya".
Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da "tallace-tallacen farfaganda"
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafi hudu a jaridar Amurka da ke bayyana amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da karin kudin China Daily a jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, bayan da ya zargi China da tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, wanda China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an kasar suka bayyana a Reuters a matsayin wani sabon mataki na yakin da Washington ke yi na matsawa kasar Sin.
Duk da cewa al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su fitar da sanarwa don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin cinikayya da ke kara tsanantawa saboda daidaita haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
Masana harkokin Sin da Amurka sun ce, takunkumin da kasar Sin ta dauka a farkon yakin cinikayya an tsara shi ne don cutar da masu fitar da kayayyaki daga jihohi kamar Iowa, wanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa.
A wani rahoto da Branstad ya rubuta a cikin jaridar Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, ya bayyana cewa China "tana kara tsananta wannan kamfen na cin zarafi ta hanyar yada tallace-tallace a cikin jaridar Amurka kyauta".
"A cikin yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da al'adar Amurka ta 'yancin faɗar albarkacin baki da' yancin manema labarai ta hanyar buga wata sanarwa ta biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, a cikin gidan jaridar da ke ƙarshen wannan titin a Beijing, akwai 'yan ra'ayoyi masu banbanci kaɗan kuma ba a ganin ainihin ra'ayoyin da Sinawa za su iya yi game da mummunan yanayin tattalin arzikin China, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin babban yatsan jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta China", in ji shi.
Ya kuma ce "wani daga cikin manyan jaridu a kasar Sin ya ki amincewa da bayar da shawarar buga" labarinsa, duk da cewa bai tabbatar da jaridar da ya rubuta ba.
Wannan bala'in da Kavanaugh ya yi ya sa mata 'yan Republican suka rasa kuri'unsu kwanaki kadan bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara
Duk da cewa yawancin manyan 'yan Republican suna goyon baya da kare dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh duk da zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin za a fuskanci tashin hankali, musamman daga mata masu jefa kuri'a, a zaben da ke tafe.
Sakamakon wannan zargi ya kasance mai yawa kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun tsaya don ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za a iya kawar da waɗannan abubuwan ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse a wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Lahadi a The Hill.
Reeher ya kuma ce yana shakkar cewa lokacin karshe na Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) don binciken FBI zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a masu fushi.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, kuma ba za su manta da shi ba a nan gaba ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn, a Washington, D.C. Daily a ranar Juma'a.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu adawa da "Nuwamba tana gabatowa!" sun yi zanga-zanga a cikin zauren Majalisar Dattawa, yayin da 'yan Republican, tare da kula da Kwamitin Shari'a, suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh, duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ya ruwaito.
"Mokokarin da ake da shi da kuma himmar 'yan Democrat zai wuce duk wani tsammanin", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai nazarin siyasa mai tsaka tsaki.
"Gaskiya ne, ya riga ya tsayi,
amma har yanzu akwai masu yawa, musamman ma tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a unguwannin da ke kusa da unguwar ko kuma tsakanin shekaru 18 zuwa 29, wadanda ko da yake ba sa son shugaban kasa, ba sa yawan zuwa kuri'a".
Kafin shaidar jama'a ta Ford ta yi bayani game da zargin da ake yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli, masu sharhi sun nuna cewa zai yiwu a sami mummunan sakamako idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatarwa.
"Wannan ya zama bala'i ga Jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon nan a NBC News.
"Wannan ya wuce batun zaben kwamitin, ko na karshe ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai zauna a kan kujera ko a'a.
Duk da haka, jama'ar Amurka sun rabu tsakanin ko za su yarda da shaidar Ford ko Kavanaugh, ko da yake sun fi son goyon bayan Kavanaugh.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin ɗari na waɗanda aka yi wa binciken sun gaskata ko kuma sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, idan aka kwatanta da kashi 35 cikin ɗari da suka goyi bayan shaidar Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun gaskata cewa Kavanaugh zai iya yin ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, idan aka kwatanta da kashi 30 cikin ɗari da suka gaskata cewa Ford ya yi ƙarya.
Bayan matsin lamba daga Flake, FBI a halin yanzu tana binciken tuhumar da Ford ya gabatar, da kuma akalla wata mai gabatar da kara, Deborah Ramirez, in ji The Guardian.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade lokacin da take da shekaru 17.
A akasin wannan, Ramirez ya yi iƙirarin cewa dan takarar Kotun Koli ya nuna mata al'aura a wani bikin kwaleji lokacin da take karatu a Yale a cikin 1980s.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai fadi yana son samar da sabuwar intanet da zata gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta yanar gizo, ya kaddamar da wani kamfani don gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Inrupt, sabon aikin wannan almara na fasaha, kamfani ne wanda ya dogara da Solid, dandamali na tushen budewa na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za su adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda za su iya samun damar abin da ke ciki.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi hasashen cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi hakan", in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu "kayan ajiyar bayanan sirri na kan layi" ko POD.
Za su iya haɗa da jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da ba a yi ba, kalandarku, kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar guda a lokaci guda.
Abin da ya sa wannan wurin ajiyar bayanan sirri ya zama na musamman shi ne cewa mai amfani yana da cikakken iko a kan wanda zai iya samun damar abin da ke ciki.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafawa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar shugabanta John Bruce, shine kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewa masu dacewa don taimakawa tabbatar da cewa an sami Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin a halin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani kamfanin tsaro na IBM, wasu masu haɓaka da aka ɗauke su aiki a kan aikin da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu haɓakawa a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba da kansu tare da kayan aikin da ke kan shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya bayyana cewa shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da "Facebook ko Google game da ko za su gabatar da cikakken canji wanda zai canza tsarin kasuwancin su daga rana zuwa rana.
"Ba mu bukatar izininka".
A cikin wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar a Medium, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "Mashin Inrupt shine samar da wutar lantarki ta kasuwanci da kuma yanayin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizo mai ƙarfi".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet ta hanyar kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya zama babbar murya a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da a lokacin da aka kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee ya ci gaba da zama mai kafa da kuma darektan Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, da kuma kungiyoyin Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa game da wannan sabon zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Taya murna ga Bernard Vann, wani limami wanda aka ba da lambar yabo ta Victoria a yakin duniya na farko
Limamin cocin Ingila daya tilo da aka ba da lambar yabo ta Victoria a lokacin yakin duniya na farko ya sami girmamawa bayan mutuwarsa a garinsu shekaru 100 bayan haka.
An ba da lambar yabo ga Lieutenant Colonel da Reverend Bernard Vann a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a lokacin da aka kai farmaki a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Duk da haka, an kashe shi ne daga wani mai harbi kwanaki hudu bayan haka ba tare da sanin cewa an ba shi lambar yabo ta soja mafi girma a Birtaniya ba.
A ranar Asabar, jikokinsa biyu sun kasance masu kula da gano wani abin tunawa a cikin girmamawa a cikin wani biki a Rushden (Northamptonshire).
Michael Vann, ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, ya nuna alamar gano wannan abin tunawa daidai shekaru 100 bayan aikin kakansa wanda ya ba shi lakabi.
A cewar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa ta hanyar Saint-Quentin Canal "ta hanyar hazo mai zurfi da kuma ƙarƙashin makamai masu linzami".
Daga baya ya yi gaggawa ya isa layin wuta kuma, tare da "babban ƙarfin hali", ya jagoranci layin gaba kafin ya hau kan bindiga ba tare da taimakon kowa ba, ya kashe mutane uku daga cikin rukunin abokan gaba.
An kashe Lt. Col. Vann ne daga wani dan bindiga na Jamus a ranar 4 ga watan Oktoba, 1918, wata daya kafin a kawo karshen yakin.
Michael Vann, ɗan shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan kakansa "wani abu ne da ba zan taɓa rayuwa da shi ba, amma darasi ne duk da haka".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr James Vann sun kuma sanya wani fure bayan bikin, wanda ya jagoranci ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial.
Michael Vann ya ce yana jin "girma sosai don shiga cikin faretin" kuma ya kara da cewa "gwargwadon wannan jarumi na gaskiya ya nuna goyon bayan mutane da yawa".
Peppa Pig ta yanke wa masu sha'awar MMA a lokacin da ya fi dacewa
Ka yi tunanin cewa ka yi barci dukan dare don ka ji daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Bellator 206 kuma lokacin da mafi kyawun lokaci ya zo wani abu ya hana ka.
San Jose ya ƙunshi gwagwarmaya 13, shida daga cikinsu manyan, kuma ana watsa su kai tsaye a Burtaniya akan Channel 5.
Amma a karfe 6 na safe, lokacin da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald za su fuskanci juna, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamakin ganin Peppa Pig ya bayyana.
Wasu ba su ji daɗi ba bayan sun yi awa da yawa suna jiran ganin wasan.
Wani mai son ya bayyana sauyawar zuwa waɗannan zane-zanen yara a Twitter a matsayin "abin dariya mai ban dariya".
"Dokar jihar ta ce wannan abun bai dace da karfe 6 na safe ba, don haka an canza shi zuwa shirye-shiryen yara", in ji Dave Schwartz, babban mataimakin shugaban kasuwanci da sadarwa na Bellator, lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da watsa shirye-shiryen.
"Peppa Pig, wannan shi ne".
Scott Coker, shugaban Bellator, ya ce za su yi la'akari da masu kallo na Birtaniya a cikin shirye-shiryen gaba.
"Ina tsammanin za mu iya magance shi idan muka yi tunani game da maimaitawa", in ji Coker.
"Amma idan yana da 6 na safe a can, ba za mu iya warware shi ba sai Lahadi, wanda zai zama Litinin a gare su.
Amma muna aiki don samun mafita.
Sa'ad da na soma samun saƙonni da yawa, ba duka ne suke da kyau ba.
Muna kokarin gyara shi ne saboda mun yi tunanin cewa wata matsala ce ta fasaha.
Amma a'a, matsalar gwamnati ce.
Na yi alkawari ba zai sake faruwa ba.
Mun yanke shawarar cewa za mu yi wasanni biyar ne kawai maimakon shida, kuma muna so mu ba wa magoya bayanmu damar da za su iya yi, amma mun wuce gona da iri.
"Wannan ya sa mu fushi sosai".
Tom Daley ya ji ya zama ƙasa saboda jima'i
Tom Daley, mai tsalle-tsalle na Olympics, ya ce ya girma yana jin cewa ya fi kowa daraja saboda jima'i, amma hakan ya sa ya sami ƙarfin gwiwa don yin nasara.
Wannan ɗan wasa mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci cewa ba kowa ba ne kamarsa ba sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare.
Baƙon da aka gabatar a farkon shirin Desert Island Discs na Radio 4 wanda Lauren Laverne ya jagoranci, ya bayyana cewa ya fara magana game da haƙƙin 'yan luwadi don ba da bege ga wasu.
Ya kuma bayyana cewa zama uba ya taimaka masa ya rage muhimmancin lashe gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, wadda ta saba gabatar da wannan shirin, ta yi rashin lafiya.
A matsayin bako na shirin farko da Laverne ya jagoranci, Daley ya raba cewa yana jin "ƙananan" ga sauran mutane saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba cewa yana son yara maza da mata".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, wannan halin na rashin cancanta da bambancin da nake da shi ne ya motsa ni kuma ya ba ni ƙarfin yin nasara".
Ina so in nuna cewa ni mutum ne don kada mutane su yi baƙin ciki sa'ad da suka gano cewa ni mutum ne.
Tare da lambobin zinare na Olympics guda biyu, ya zama babban mai fafutukar LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da bayyanarsa a wasannin Commonwealth na Australiya don kiran ƙarin ƙasashe don dakatar da luwadi.
Ta yanke shawarar yin magana ne domin ta ji cewa ta yi sa'a da za ta iya rayuwa a fili ba tare da tsoron wani sakamako ba, kuma tana son ta ba wasu bege.
Gwarzon zakaran duniya sau uku ya ce ya yi soyayya da Dustin Lance Black, wani fim din Amurka, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013, "baƙon abu ne".
Daley ta auri wannan ɗan wasan Oscar a bara kuma ta ce shekarunsu 20 ba su taɓa zama matsala ba.
"Idan ka rayu sosai a cikin ɗan lokaci" (yana ɗan shekara 14 a lokacin da ya halarci gasar Olympics ta farko kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka), yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan'uwa da ya kai shekarunka da ya taɓa fuskantar irin wannan yanayin.
Ma'auratan sun haifi ɗansu na fari a watan Yuni, Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma wannan haihuwar ta sa Daley ya canza ra'ayinsa gaba ɗaya.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, babbar motsawa ta ita ce lashe zinare", in ji ta.
"Amma yanzu na san cewa akwai abubuwa da yawa da suka fi zinari na zinariya na Olympics muhimmanci.
A gare ni, lambar yabo ita ce Robbie".
An haifi ɗansa bayan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a 2011 yana da shekaru 40 daga ciwon daji na kwakwalwa.
Mahaifin Daley bai yarda cewa zai mutu ba, kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambayi dansa shine wasu tikiti zuwa London 2012, yana so ya kasance a gaban layi.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa cewa ba zan kasance a nan don ɗaukar wannan jere na farko ba", in ji Daley.
"Ina riƙe da hannunsa lokacin da ya daina numfashi kuma a wannan lokacin, lokacin mutuwarsa, na fahimci cewa ba a iya cin nasara da shi ba", in ji ta.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ya yi gasa a gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe lambar tagulla.
"A wannan lokacin na san cewa wannan shine burina na rayuwa: tsalle a gaban taron jama'a a ƙasata don shiga gasar Olympics, babu wani abin da ya fi wannan jin daɗi", in ji ta.
Zaɓin Heather Small na Proud ba shi da amfani, tun da yake shi ne waƙar da ta bi ta lokacin da ta shirya don gasar Olympics kuma har yanzu yana sa gashinsa.
Desert Island Discs a tashar BBC Radio 4, ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 na BST.
Wani Mickelson da ya yi kasa da kima ya fadi a kan kujerar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47 a ranar Lahadi, amma zai bukaci inganta fasaharsa don kada wannan ya zama abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda ke halartar taron shekara biyu a karo na 12, ya tsaya a kan benci saboda shawarar kyaftin Jim Furyk kuma bai iya shiga wasannin hudu ko kuma wasannin foursomes na ranar Asabar ba.
Maimakon zama cibiyar aiki, kamar yadda sau da yawa a Amurka, zakaran sau biyar ya ciyar da rana yana motsawa da kuma inganta ayyukansa.
Ko da yake bai kasance mafi ƙarancin 'yan wasa ba, ko da a lokacin da ya fi dacewa da aikinsa, a shekara ta 48 ba ya dace da filin wasa na Le Golf National, inda tsayi mai tsayi ya azabtar da kuskuren da ya faru.
Kuma idan hakan bai isa ba, Mickelson zai fafata a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi da Francesco Molinari, wanda ya lashe gasar Open ta Burtaniya, wanda ya hada kai da Tommy Fleetwood don lashe wasanni hudu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa, da suka yi kasa da maki hudu a wasan farko na wasanni 12, suka fara da kyau, Mickelson zai iya zama mai mahimmanci.
Furyk ya amince da mijinta, ko da yake ba zai iya faɗi kome ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci rawar da nake takawa a yau, ya bugi kafaɗata, ya ba ni hannu ya ce zan kasance a shirye gobe".
"Ya kasance mai cikakken tabbaci.
Yana da babban wuri a cikin Hall of Fame kuma ya ba da gudummawa sosai ga ƙungiyoyi a baya da wannan makon.
Wataƙila ba ta yi tunanin cewa ta buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tsammanin zan yi wasa sosai, amma a ƙarshe wannan shi ne yadda abubuwa suke kuma wannan shine yadda muke tsammanin ya kamata.
Kamar kowa, yana so ya fita waje".
A ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai doke Nick Faldo a mafi yawan wasannin da aka buga a gasar Ryder.
Zai iya nuna ƙarshen aikinsa a gasar Ryder Cup, aikin da bai taɓa kaiwa matakin sa ba.
