Shugaban Turai, Thomas Bjorn, yana tsoron cewa zai rasa ragamarsa
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din Turai, ya san ta hanyar kwarewa cewa babban ci gaba a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup na iya zama tafiya mai wahala.
Dan Danish din ya fara ne a 1997 a wasan da aka yi a Valderrama, inda tawagar da Seve Ballesteros ya jagoranci ta samu maki biyar a kan Amurkawa, amma sun kai ga ƙarshen layi tare da nasara ta hanyar cin nasara 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Kuna tunanin cewa muna da babban fa'ida a Valderrama; kamar a Brookline, inda muka yi asara, amma a Valderrama mun ci nasara kaɗan", in ji Bjorn, a cikin hoton, bayan ya ga nasarar 2018 ta ci 5-3 a ranar Juma'a da, jiya, 10-6 a Le Golf National.
Tarihi ya nuna cewa wannan ba ta ƙare ba tukuna.
Dole ne mu tafi mu same su duka gobe.
Dole ne ku fita kuma ku yi abin da ke daidai.
