Jamus ta sabon warship jinkirta sake
An shirya sabon jirgin ruwan na rundunar sojan ruwa ta Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba zai isa ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma karuwar kudin, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
An jinkirta shigar da Rheinland-Pfalz, babban jirgin ruwan Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, in ji wani kakakin soja ga jaridar Die Zeit.
An shirya jirgin ruwa don shiga cikin Navy a 2014, amma matsalolin da aka samu bayan bayarwa sun shafi makomar wannan shiri mai girma.
Jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg guda hudu, wanda Rundunar Sojan Sama ta ba da umarni a shekara ta 2007, za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An fahimci cewa za su sami babban bindiga, tare da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami, da kuma fasaha mai ɓoyewa, irin su radar da aka rage, infrared da sautin sauti.
Sauran muhimman fasali sun hada da tsawon lokacin kulawa, ya kamata ya yiwu a tura sababbin jiragen ruwa har zuwa shekaru biyu a waje da tashar jiragen ruwa.
Duk da haka, kamar yadda Die Zeit ta nuna, waɗannan jinkirin ci gaba suna nufin cewa jiragen ruwa na zamani tare da sabuwar fasaha, wanda zai ba Jamus damar nuna ikonta a ƙasashen waje, za su zama tsofaffi lokacin da suka shiga sabis.
An yi ta buga labarin jirgin ruwan F125 a bara, lokacin da rundunar sojan ruwan Jamus ta ki amincewa da shi kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa gidan ginin jirgin ruwa na Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ruwa ta mayar da jirgi ga mai gina shi bayan an ba da shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka dawo da shi ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun yi magana game da "ƙananan lahani a cikin software da hardware" wanda ya hana amfani da jirgin ruwa a cikin aikin yaki.
Rashin software ya kasance mai mahimmanci, tun da yake jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg za su yi aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120; wato, rabin ma'aikatan da ake bukata a tsohuwar jirgin ruwa na Bremen.
Bugu da ƙari, an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyin nauyi mai yawa, wanda ya rage aikinsa kuma ya iyakance ikon Navy don ƙara haɓakawa a nan gaba.
An yi imanin cewa Rheinland-Pfalz mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin jirage iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Baya ga kayan aiki mara kyau, yawan kuɗin aikin, wanda ya haɗa da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin, yana zama matsala.
An ce ya riga ya kai dala biliyan 3.1, idan aka kwatanta da biliyan 2.2 da aka fara.
Matsalar da ke tattare da sababbin jiragen ruwa na da muhimmanci musamman a yayin da ake gargadin cewa sojojin Jamus na ruwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin kare dangi na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa suna da karancin jiragen ruwa da za su iya turawa.
Jami'in ya ce wannan matsala tana kara girma, saboda an cire tsofaffin jiragen ruwa, amma ba a maye gurbinsu da wasu ba.
Ya kuma yi nadamar cewa babu wani daga cikin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da zai iya shiga cikin Navy.
