Kifi da noma sune manyan ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Har ila yau, ma'adinan nickel suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a gefen tekun da ke gaba da Celebes.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami kuma ya shafi yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan yankin Pacific Fire Belt mai yawan girgizar kasa, saboda haka tana fama da girgizar kasa akai-akai.
Waɗannan su ne wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia, a arewacin Sumatra, wanda ya faru a ranar 26 ga Disamba, ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi, a Aceh.
2005: An yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya lalata gabar teku ta kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afku a tsibirin Mentawai, wanda ke gabashin Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsayi har mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa mai rauni ta afkawa lardin Pidie Jaya da ke Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici yayin da mutane ke tunawa da bala'in da girgizar kasa da tsunami ta 2004 ta haifar.
A wannan lokacin babu tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu saboda faduwar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a tsibirin yawon bude ido na Indonesiya na Lombok, wanda ya yi sanadin mutuwar mutane sama da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin gida na ɗan lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin mata
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi da laifin hari.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, dan asalin Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin aikata laifukan tashin hankali a cikin gida, hana bayar da rahoton tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma adawa da hukuma, a cewar wata sanarwa da jami'an 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka fitar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce, lokacin da wata abokiyarta ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don kai rahoton zargin aikata laifuka, ya karɓi wayar daga hannun ta.
Palin tana tsare a gidan yari a Mat-Su Pretrial Facility a kan belin dala 500, KTUU ta ruwaito.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya bayyana "ba shi da laifi, ba tare da wata shakka ba" lokacin da aka tambaye shi, in ji gidan yarin.
Palin tana fuskantar manyan laifuffuka uku na Class A, wanda ke nufin za ta iya shiga kurkuku har shekara guda da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ya shafi 'yancin kai, wanda ake iya yankewa a gidan yari har kwana daya da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka gabatar da tuhumar aikata laifi a kan Palin ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017, an zarge shi da kai hari ga mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don kai rahoton zargin da ake yi.
Yanzu haka dai ana shari'ar ne a kotun Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin gida, hana gabatar da rahoton tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma mallakar makamai cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta zarge shi da dūkan fuskarsa.
Sarah Palin ta fuskanci suka daga kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji a shekarar 2016 bayan ta danganta halin tashin hankalin danta da ciwon tashin hankali bayan da ya yi aiki a Iraki.
Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun kashe daruruwan mutane a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 sun mutu bayan girgizar kasa da ta afku a tsibirin Indonesiya na Celebes a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya lalata dubban gidaje.
Ba a samun wutar lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa, kuma ana sa ran adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai karu da kwanaki.
Girgizar ta afku ne a gabashin birnin Jakarta na kasar Indonesia.
Akwai bidiyon da ke yawo a shafukan sada zumunta da ke nuna lokacin da ya faru.
Daruruwan mutane sun hallara a wani biki a bakin rairayin bakin teku a garin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya afku a gabar teku.
A wasu lokuta ana amfani da hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna kokarin yanke hukuncin kisa akan Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a yankewa jihar ba tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan hanyar West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da keke da ya samu a hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe duk wadanda aka kashe "da gangan" kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka gabatar a gundumar kudu ta New York.
Dukkanin laifuffukan biyu suna da yiwuwar hukuncin kisa bisa ga takardar kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai tare da ƙungiyar aikata laifuka, aikin da ake amfani da shi a lokuta masu aikata laifuka, da kuma aikata laifuka biyu na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi da gangan", in ji masu gabatar da kara yayin da suke bayanin yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da "mummunan, mummunan aiki da lalata" harin.
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da asarar dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco" kamar yadda sanarwar sanarwar ta bayyana.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Kusan shekaru goma kenan da Kudancin New York ba ta yi shari'ar kisa ba.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan wasu 'yan dillalan miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
An yi amfani da hukuncin kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya a New York a shekarar 1953 a cikin Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa don yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg a cikin kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nadama a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗi game da abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya dauki bidiyon ISIS da ya kalli a wayarsa ne ya sa ya kai harin.
Ya kuma nemi a ba shi damar ganin tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan wasu laifuffuka 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya nuna cewa sun kasance "mai takaici" game da hukuncin da ake tuhuma.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karɓar hukuncin kisa tare da ɗaurin rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai ƙara tsawon lokacin da waɗannan abubuwan suka haifar ga duk waɗanda ke da hannu", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta bukaci masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Wani dan majalisa na Tory ya ce ya kamata a sa Nigel Farage a kan gaba wajen tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "tallafawa mutane sojoji" a yau a wani zanga-zanga a taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar Independence Party ya ce 'yan siyasa suna bukatar su "ji matsin lamba" daga masu shakkar Turai (lokacin da wani dan majalisa na Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata ya dauki nauyin tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisa Peter Bone ya bayyana a gaban masu zanga-zangar Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta riga ta fice daga EU idan Mr Farage ne sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta na sulhunta bangarorin jam'iyyarta ya bayyana a yayin da 'yan Tory masu goyon bayan ci gaba da kasancewa a EU suka shiga zanga-zangar 'yancin kai ta Brexit a birnin.
Firaministan kasar na fama da ci gaba da aiwatar da alkawuran da ta dauka a shirin ta na Chequers a yayin da masu goyon bayan Brexit da masu adawa da ita da kuma EU ke kai mata farmaki.
Abokansa sun nace cewa ya ci gaba da gwagwarmaya don ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya tare da Brussels duk da amsa mara kyau, don tilasta masu shakka da ma'aikatan aiki su zabi tsakanin shirinsa da hargitsi.
Mr Bone ya bayyana a taron 'yan adawa na Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana son kawo karshen shirin Chequers.
Ya ce ya kamata a sa ran Mr Farage ya dauki nauyin tattaunawar da aka yi da Brussels.
Da an ba shi mukamin, da mun riga mun fita daga EU a yanzu, in ji shi.
Dan majalisar dokokin Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan ci gaba da goyon bayan Brexit, amma dole ne mu soke shirin Chequers".
A cikin nuna adawarsa ga EU, ya bayyana cewa: "Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don mu zama masu amfani ba.
Muna son yin dokokinmu a kasarmu.
Mista Bone ya musanta shawarwarin da ke nuna cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun bayan zaben 2016: "Gaskiyar cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayi kuma suna son ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin EU ba gaskiya bane".
'Yan majalisa na Tory da kuma Brexit Andrea Jenkyns sun halarci gangamin, inda ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Abin da kawai nake cewa shi ne: Firayim Minista, ku saurari jama'a.
Shirin Chequers ba shi da kyau a tsakanin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su zabe shi ba, ba shi da kyau a tsakanin jam'iyyarmu da masu fafutukarmu wadanda suka fara zama a kan tituna kuma suka ba mu damar zama zaɓaɓɓu.
Ka soke shirin Chequers kuma ka fara sauraro.
A wata wasikar da ya aika wa Mrs May, ya kara da cewa: "Firai ministoci suna rike da ayyukansu idan suka cika alkawuransu".
Mr Farage ya ce a taron cewa ya zama dole a "ji dadi" ga 'yan siyasa idan suna da niyyar cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
A halin yanzu wannan batun amana ne tsakanin mu, mutane, da kuma tsarin siyasarmu, in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar shawarar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu cewa ba za mu bar su su fita da nasu ba".
A wani sako da ya aika wa masu sauraro, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so ku sa 'yan siyasarmu, wadanda ke gab da cin amanar shawarar Brexit, su ji dadi.
"Muna tattara sojojin mutanen wannan kasa da suka ba mu nasara a Brexit kuma ba za su huta ba har sai mun zama Burtaniya mai alfahari, mai zaman kanta da kuma cin gashin kanta".
A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin EU sun yi tafiya a Birmingham kafin su gudanar da taron sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun yi amfani da takardun shaida tare da sakon Tories Against Brexit bayan da aka kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
A lokacin taron, shugaban jam'iyyar Labour, Lord Adonis, ya yi ba'a ga 'yan majalisa game da matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta a cikin wani shiri na jam'iyyar.
"Waɗannan mutane ne ke gaya mana cewa za su iya samun tsarin IT da kyau da kuma duk mafi kyawun fasaha don Kanada, don samun iyakar da ba ta da ƙyama, don jin daɗin kasuwa mai kyau ba tare da iyaka a Ireland ba", in ji shi.
Wannan ba gaskiya ba ne.
Ya kara da cewa, "babu wani abu mai kyau kamar Brexit".
Warren na shirin yin tunani sosai game da neman shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa dan jam'iyyar Democrat daga Massachusetts ya yi magana game da makomar sa a ranar Asabar yayin taron gari a wani yanki a yammacin Massachusetts.
Warren, wanda ya saba sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, zai sake tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa a watan Nuwamba da Geoff Diehl na Republican, wanda ya jagoranci yakin neman zaben Trump a shekarar 2016 a Massachusetts.
Ta kasance cibiyar hasashe game da matsayin ta a matsayin magajin Trump a 2020.
Taron na ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shine taronsa na 36 da masu jefa kuri'a ta amfani da tsarin gari tun lokacin da Trump ya hau mulki.
Wani mataimaki ya tambaye shi ko yana shirin tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su magance matsalolin gwamnatinmu, kuma hakan na bukatar mace a matsayin shugaban kasa.
An kama wani mutum dangane da harin da aka yi wa Sims, dan wasan LSU
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, L.A., sun sanar a ranar Asabar cewa an kama wani da ake zargi da kisan Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwando na LSU a ranar Juma'a.
Ma'aikatar 'yan sanda ta Baton Rouge ta sanar da kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, a wani taron manema labarai da aka yi da karfe 11:00 na yammacin yamma.
Sun wallafa wani bidiyo na harbi a ranar Juma'a suna neman taimako wajen gano mutumin da ke cikin hotunan.
An kashe Sims, mai shekara 20, a kusa da jami'ar Southern a safiyar ranar Juma'a.
Wayde Sims ya ji rauni ne daga harsashin bindiga a kansa kuma daga karshe ya mutu sakamakon hakan, in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul ga kafofin yada labarai a ranar Asabar ta hanyar 247sports.
Wayde ya tsaya don kare abokinsa kuma Simpson ya harbe shi.
Simpson ya amsa tambayoyin da aka yi masa kuma ya yarda da kasancewa a wurin da makami kuma ya yarda da harbi Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da an yi wani abu ba kuma an tsare shi a ofishin 'yan sanda na yankin Baton Rouge.
Sims, wani matashi mai tsayi shida wanda ya girma a Baton Rouge, ya buga wasanni 32 tare da farawa 10 a kakar wasa ta ƙarshe kuma ya kasance yana da kimanin minti 17.4, 5.6 da 2.9 a kowace wasa.
Gasar Rasha: Lewis Hamilton ya kusanci taken duniya saboda umarnin ƙungiyar, wanda ya ba shi damar cin nasara akan Sebastian Vettel
Ya bayyana tun lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya yi nasara a gaban Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar cewa umarnin ƙungiyar Mercedes zai zama mai yanke hukunci a tseren.
Bottas, wanda ya fara daga kan hanya, ya yi kyakkyawan farawa kuma ya kusan barin Hamilton shi kaɗai yayin da yake kare matsayinsa a cikin zagaye biyu na farko kuma yana gayyatar Vettel ya kai wa abokin aikinsa hari.
Vettel ya fara shiga akwatunan farko kuma ya bar Hamilton ya yi tsere tare da zirga-zirga a ƙarshen rukuni, wani abu da zai zama mai mahimmanci.
Mercedes ta tsaya a cikin akwatin jirgi bayan wani lokaci kuma ta fita a bayan Vettel, amma Hamilton ya wuce shi bayan da yawa da yawa da ke motsawa da ke motsawa wanda ya sa direban Ferrari ya bar cikin gida ba tare da son rai ba don fuskantar haɗarin kasancewa a baya bayan sau biyu a cikin kari na uku.
Max Verstappen ya fara daga jere na karshe na layin fara wasa kuma ya hau zuwa matsayi na bakwai a ƙarshen zagaye na farko a ranar haihuwarsa ta 21.
