Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi wa Sanata Dianne Feinstein ba'a a wani taron da aka yi a ranar Asabar saboda dagewarta kan cewa ba ta fallasa wasikar Christine Blasey Ford ba, wacce ta zargi dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh da cin zarafin mata.
A wani jawabi da ya yi a wani taron a West Virginia, shugaban bai yi magana kai tsaye game da shaidar da Ford ya bayar a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa ba, kuma ya yi sharhi a maimakon haka cewa abin da ke faruwa a majalisar dattijai ya nuna cewa mutane "masu banƙyama ne, masu banƙyama da maƙaryaci".
