Ƙungiyar Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallo biyu a raga a wasan da Giants ta yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun shawo kan rashin nasarar da suka sha a gasar Elite ta ranar Juma'a da Belfast Giants ta hanyar lashe wasan da aka yi a ranar Asabar 5-3 a Dundee.
Giants sun samu nasara a farkon wasan da suka ci Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita a cikin gida kafin Dwyer ya sake kafa Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya tashi tsaye a Dundee kafin kwallo biyu daga Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ba su damar cin nasara.
Wannan ne karo na uku da aka yi a gasar Elite League a wannan kakar wasan da Adam Keefe ya yi, inda suka samu nasarar doke Dundee da ci 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a da yamma.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin biyu ke karawa a kakar bana, inda suka ci gaba da cin nasara a wasanni uku da suka gabata.
An fara wasan farko na Dwyer a minti na 3:35 ta hanyar taimakon Kendall McFaull, kuma na biyu ya zo minti hudu daga Beauvillier bayan taimakon David Rutherford.
A cikin wani lokaci mai wahala, Sullivan ya sake shigar da 'yan wasan gida a wasan a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya taimaka wa Cownie don zira kwallo a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun ci gaba a cikin ci gaban kafin hutu na farko lokacin da ya zira kwallo ta biyu a daren a ƙarshen zangon farko.
Kungiyar gida ta sake haɗuwa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaita wasan tare da burin da aka buga ta hanyar wasan wuta a minti 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun hada kai don taimakawa Nielsen ta ci Dundee a wasan farko a karshen zangon biyu kuma ta tabbatar da nasara ta hanyar cin nasarar ta biyar a tsakiyar zangon karshe.
Giants, wadanda suka rasa wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka buga a yanzu, za su buga wasansu na gaba a gida a Milton Keynes ranar Juma'a.
Wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ya mutu don tabbatar da cewa daruruwan fasinjojin jirgin sama za su iya tserewa daga girgizar kasa
Wani mai kula da jirgin sama a Indonesia da aka yi wa lakabi da gwarzo bayan ya mutu don tabbatar da cewa jirgin da ke dauke da daruruwan fasinjoji ya tashi lafiya.
Yawan mutanen da suka mutu ya kai 800 kuma da yawa sun bace bayan wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, inda ta haifar da tsunami.
