Ta yaya yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai zama mai kyau ga Beijing
An fara harin bam din yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China da zafi, kuma duk da cewa yakin bai kai ga ƙarshe ba, ƙwararrun masana sun ce nisantar da kasashen biyu na iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara ba da gargadi a farkon wannan shekarar yana sanya takunkumi kan manyan kayayyakin da ake fitarwa daga China, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminum.
Mafi girman tashin hankali ya zo ne a wannan makon tare da sabon haraji wanda ya shafi kwatankwacin dala biliyan 200, yana ɗaukar rabin kayan da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
Beijing ta mayar da martani a kowane lokaci, mafi kwanan nan ta ƙara haraji daga kashi biyar zuwa kashi goma akan kayayyakin Amurkawa na dala biliyan 60.
China ta yi alkawarin yin koyi da matakan Amurka kuma ba zai yiwu tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ya yi watsi da hakan ba nan ba da jimawa ba.
Don samun Washington ta yi baya, zai zama wajibi ne a yi biyayya ga bukatunsu, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a fili zai zama mafi kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta san yadda za ta yi amfani da katunan da suka dace, matsin lamba daga yakin cinikayya da Amurka na iya taimaka wa China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa yanke shawara na siyasa da sauri a Washington ko Beijing zai iya haifar da yanayin da ake buƙata don fara rikicin tattalin arziki a ƙasashen biyu ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda aka sani", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike a Asiya a Cibiyar Nazarin Sabuwar Amurka.
Syria ta shirya 'da 'yan gudun hijirar su dawo, in ji ministan harkokin wajen kasar
Siriya ta ce a shirye take ta karɓi 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina ƙasar da ta ɓarnatar da ita bayan yaƙi na shekaru bakwai.
A jawabin da ya gabatar a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ministan harkokin waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin kasar na samun sauki.
"A yau yanayin da ke ƙasa ya fi karko da tsaro saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaƙi da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da al'amura cikin sauki.
Yanzu an samar da dukkan abubuwan da ake bukata don dawowar 'yan gudun hijirar da suka bar kasarsu saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na kai tsaye wanda ya shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da mutane miliyan 5.5 ne suka tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da aka fara yakin a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida suna zaune a kasar kuma suna bukatar agajin jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi godiya da duk wani taimako da za ta samu don sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba zai yarda da taimako ba tare da wani sharadi ba ko daga kasashen da ke goyon bayan tawayen.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a birnin Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 ta doke kungiyar Amurka da ta zira kwallaye 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a kulob din Le Golf National da ke kusa da birnin Paris, Faransa.
Wannan ne karo na shida da Amurka ta ci nasara a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe gasar a lokacin da tawagar Denmark ta Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da ta buƙaci don doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya fi yawan gwagwarmaya a gasar, ya jefa kwallon cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na par 3, ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Gasar ta Italiya ta yi fice a dukkan wasanninta, ta zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasan golf huɗu da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
An doke dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth 5&4 daga hannun dan wasan da ya fi kasa da kowa a gasar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Mai darajar duniya Dustin Johnson ya sha kashi 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda zai iya buga gasar Ryder ta karshe.
Wani tsohon soja da ya lashe gasar Ryder Cup guda takwas, Sergio Garcia na Spain ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi yawan nasara a gasar, tare da 25.5 maki.
"Ba na yawan kuka, amma a yau ba zan iya guje wa hakan ba.
Shekara ce mai wahala.
Ina matukar godiya ga Thomas da ya zaba ni kuma ya yi imani da ni.
Ina farin ciki, ina farin cikin samun kofin.
Abu mai mahimmanci shine ƙungiyar, kuma ina farin cikin taimaka wa", in ji Garcia mai farin ciki bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya mika shaidar ga dan kasarsa John Ram, wanda ya yi nasarar doke Tiger Woods da ci 2 da 1 a wasan da aka yi a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm, mai shekara 23, ya ce: "Ina alfahari sosai da yadda na ci Tiger Woods a wasan da na yi a lokacin.
Woods ya rasa wasanninsa hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki ga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan da suka taba lashe gasar Major 14 inda yake a baya ga Jack Nicklaus.
Kungiyar Amurka ta yi ta fama da matsalar rashin fita daga tituna a duk karshen mako, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, wadanda suka buga golf mai inganci a duk gasar.
Kyaftin din Amurka, Jim Furyk, ya bayyana bayan rashin nasarar tawagarsa: "Ina alfahari da waɗannan yara, sun yi gwagwarmaya.
A wannan safiya, sun yi wa Turawa wahala na ɗan lokaci.
Mun yi yaƙi.
Na ɗauki hatimi a gaban Thomas.
Kai babban kyaftin ne.
'Yan wasansu 12 sun yi wasa sosai.
Za mu sake tsara kanmu, mu yi aiki tare da PGA na Amurka da kuma kwamitinmu na Ryder Cup, kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina son wadannan yara 12 kuma ina alfahari da zama kyaftin.
Wannan don cire hat.
Sun fi su".
Bayanan ruwa na Red tide:
Rahoton da aka bayar kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa an samu raguwar yawan ruwan teku a yankunan da ke yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar kwamitin da aka ambata, ana ganin yanayin da ke kara samun bambanci a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Collier, wanda hakan na iya nufin cewa an rage yawan ruwa.
Ruwa mai ja yana da nisan kilomita 210 daga bakin teku daga lardin Pinellas na arewa zuwa Lee na kudu.
Ana iya samun tarin mutane a cikin mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a wurare da yawa fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma sami ruwan tsami a cikin County Pasco.
An ba da rahoton matsakaitan matakan taro a cikin ko kusa da bakin teku na Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan ƙananan kuma manyan taro a kusa da bakin teku na Hillsborough County, ƙananan ƙananan taro a cikin ko kusa da bakin teku na Sarasota County, ƙananan ƙananan taro a Charlotte County, ƙananan ƙananan taro a cikin ko kusa da bakin teku tare da Lee County, da ƙananan taro a cikin Collier County.
A cikin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier County an ba da rahoton ci gaba da samun cututtukan numfashi.
Babu wani irin wannan lamarin da aka ruwaito a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
